<item>
            <title>[CXF-3845] Incompatibility between Derby 10.8 and WS-RM RMTxStore</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3845</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The RMTxStore implementation does not work with Derby versions 10.8 and higher due to a bugfix for &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4965&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4965&lt;/a&gt;. The issue can be reproduced by replacing the Derby version in the parent pom.xml to 10.8.1.2, afterwards some of the existing test cases for WS-RM fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix for this is rather trivial (and proposed in the Derby 10.8 release notes). I attach a patch for the trunk to this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
